{
  "stem": "628.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My uncle, he was a shikra.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was well in with the SS and with everybody.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He went to Hamburg and he must have drank a lot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he talked, and they-- they found out that his wife was a Jew, and his children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they deported them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The Mauritian was deported before us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And Rita, as well, she was picked up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She had-- but he must have properly talked against her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He must really have talked maybe against the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he was put into prison, suddenly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we hear it from his secretary who worked there, from the family, that it had happened.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Carl and Mauritian, it happened so fast.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you can imagine my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That must've been in '42.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I've got there-- in Birkenau, I found, there, what's it called, when they arrived there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when that-- maybe if that wouldn't have happened, he could have-- my uncle could have fit in us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he was quite-- quite rich family, being tailoring for the German, high officers and all that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was all smashed up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember, suddenly, later, '42 and a half, something like that, my grandparents said to me, all the jewelry they had and all of what they had, you know, bring them over to Ilk.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was the associate-- the partner for my uncle, and they should keep it for us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, grandmother, what are you talking about?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, they should keep it, and put it away somewhere in a safe place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I did that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So what happened, going back, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sometimes, when I came near my district, I had to put it on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At night time, I walked home, sudden-- suddenly somebody hit me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[GERMAN] I said, what?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was getting worse and worse.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
